---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-prose grid gap-16 py-20 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] md:items-center md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <span class="chip mb-6 border-copper-700/50 text-copper-300">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-copper-400"></span>
        Public beta
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl leading-[1.05] text-ink-50 sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl">
        Write once.<br />
        <span class="text-copper-400">Publish everywhere.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
        Draft your chaptered story once in Markdown. PawPoller generates every format and posts it to nine furry-fiction platforms — then tracks how your stories, artwork and social posts perform across fifteen.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
        <a href="#get" class="btn-primary">
          Download for Windows + Linux
          <Icon name="ph:arrow-down" class="h-4 w-4" />
        </a>
        <a href="#get" class="btn-secondary">Self-host with Docker</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller" class="text-sm text-ink-300 transition hover:text-copper-300">
          View the source →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-ink-700 bg-ink-800 shadow-glow">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-ink-700 px-4 py-2">
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-ink-700"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-ink-700"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-copper-500/80"></span>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-ink-400">MASTER.md</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="overflow-x-auto p-6 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-100"><code><span class="text-ink-500">&lt;!-- @title --&gt;</span>
<span class="text-copper-300"># Late Shift</span>

<span class="text-ink-500">&lt;!-- @subtitle --&gt;</span>
*A novella in seven chapters*

<span class="text-ink-500">&lt;!-- @byline --&gt;</span>
by Your Name

<span class="text-ink-500">&lt;!-- @body --&gt;</span>

<span class="text-copper-300">## Chapter 1: The Last Call</span>

The bar had cleared out an hour ago.
Dane was still wiping down the same
patch of counter...</code></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -inset-4 -z-10 rounded-2xl bg-copper-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
